@ShaMan239 we should adopt @GBKS suggestion as a designer, so I retract my ack. Please update the button text according to his suggestions. Below are some other suggestions related to the translator comments.

@GBKS thanks for taking the time to review a GUI PR. What you've noticed about the missing window title of a QMessageBox on macOS is the expected behavior, see: [QMessageBox::setWindowTitle](https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qmessagebox.html#setWindowTitle)

> Sets the title of the message box to title. On macOS, the window title is ignored (as required by the macOS Guidelines).

